@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wfcofd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.cos(0.06) / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.89) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.09)))
    v2 = wp.sin(0.08)
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(v0 + 0.35)) / ((v1 + 0.02 * v1 + 0.02) + (v2 + 0.42 / v2 + 0.13)))
    tmp = ((0.97 - 0.18) - (wp.cos(v1 + 0.47) / (v1 + 0.73 + v2 + 0.33)))
    tmp = 0.39
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.67) + 0.12) + (wp.sin(v2 + 0.28) - wp.exp(v2 + 0.20)))
    v0 = ((tmp * wp.cos(tmp + 0.76)) / wp.abs(0.15))
    data[tid] = v0
